New Controls Added :
To go into record mode and record parameters for frames: Press 0
To go into playback mode : Press 8
To change camera views : Press 9

Robot Orientation :
Right Arrow : Tilt transformer right
Left Arrow : Tilt left
Up arrow : Move ahead
Down arrow : Move back
6 : Tilt Down (Towards ground)
7 : Tilt up


Old Controls :

Head :
I : Translate head along y-axis


Right Leg :
S, Ctrl+S : Move right leg (complete) about z-axis (outward to the plane)
P, Ctrl+P : Rotate about x-axis
D, Ctrl+D : Translate right leg along x axis 
G, Ctrl+G : Rotate lower leg about z axis

Left Leg :
A, Ctrl+A : Move left leg (complete) about z-axis (outward to the plane)
O, Ctrl+O : Rotate about x-axis
D, Ctrl+D : Translate left leg along x axis
H, Ctrl+H : Rotate lower leg about z axis

Right Hand :
Q, Ctrl+Q : Translate along the y-axis
Z, Ctrl+Z : Translate parts of lower hand to form missiles
E, Ctrl+E : Rotate about z-axis
X, Ctrl+X : Rotate about y-axis
N, Ctrl+N : Rotate about x-axis
R, Ctrl+R : Rotate lower hand about z-axis

Left Hand :
W, Ctrl+W : Translate along the y-axis
Y, Ctrl+Y : Rotate about z-axis
2, Ctrl+2 : Rotate about y-axis
1, Ctrl+1 : Rotate about x-axis
U, Ctrl+U : Rotate lower hand about z-axis

Blades :
=, Ctrl+= : Rotate blades about y-axis
K, Ctrl+K : Translate blades out of the body (along y axis)
;, Ctrl+; : Split and open blades


Disclaimer :
The functions used to load images for texture and form the pixel array were taken directly from (with small modifications) :
http://nehe.gamedev.net/tutorial/texture_mapping/12038/
